    "## Evaluate ice-shelf velocity using ITS_LIVE data \n",
    "This notebook goes through finding monthly ice-shelf velocities at three positions on an ice shelf. For the original project, three vulnerable ice shelves in West Antarctica were analyzed: Thwaites Eastern Ice Shelf, Pine Island Glacier Ice Shelf, and Crosson Ice Shelf. For these ice shelves, a shelf-front, mid-shelf, and grounding zone position were used. \n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook can be adapted for any ice-surface speeds provided by ITS_LIVE. Visit the ITS_LIVE project widget here. "
   ]
  },
